snippet.title: Lucid Lenses - Official Trailer Video 30 seconds
snippet.description:
Follow the story of a couple who meet and fall in love. However, as they pursue their individual career dreams, they find themselves facing a difficult choice; continue their relationship or break up for the sake of their careers.
